<div class="tldr-box">
  <h3>TL;DR, the short answer for Indians</h3>
  <p>These solve different problems. Notion AI is excellent inside your Notion workspace, summarising meetings, querying databases, "ask AI" across your knowledge base. Claude is the best standalone chat for writing, analysis, and coding. If you live in Notion, Plus at ~₹997/user is a great value. If you write or code daily, Claude Pro at ~₹2,005 is your daily driver. Many Indian teams use both.</p>
</div>

<p>This is one of those comparisons where "vs" is misleading, these tools mostly don't overlap. The real question for Indian users is which problem you're trying to solve, and we'll work through that here.</p>

<h2>Quick comparison</h2>

